====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[42]
You’re saying it wasn’t?
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[43]:0,94
I’m saying I made a lot of people rich: border guards, bureaucrats, police, even the mayor.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[43]:94,247
