====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[212]:361,548
I saw something in his eyes, something I didn’t recognize, and then suddenly he was on me, a lightning whirlwind that threw me up against the wall, slapped me so hard my left ear rang.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[212]:548,658
“You WILL go!” he shouted as he grabbed my shoulders and repeatedly slammed me against the cheap drywall.
====
