====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[212]:872,989
I didn’t understand where this man had come from, this lion who’d replaced my docile, frail excuse for a parent.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[212]:989,1017
A lion protecting his cubs.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[212]:1017,1169
He knew that fear was the only weapon he had left to save my life and if I didn’t fear the threat of the plague, then dammit, I was going to fear him!
