Blood, skin, hair, saliva, even urine and feces 4 …it was exhausting, mortifying.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[221]:184,394
The only thing that made it bearable, and probably what prevented an all-out riot among some of the Muslim detainees, was that most of the doctors and nurses doing the examinations were themselves Palestinian.
====
/html/body/div/div[1]/p[221]:394,504
The doctor who examined my mother and sisters was a woman, an American woman from a place called Jersey City.
