TOPEKA, KANSAS, USA
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[27]:0,154
[Sharon could be considered beautiful by almost any standard—with long red hair, sparkling green eyes, and the body of a dancer or a prewar supermodel.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[27]:154,200
She also has the mind of a four-year-old girl.
