I had vacation days and sick days, full medical and a sweet dental package.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[92]:492,539
I paid my taxes, too much; I paid into my IRA.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[92]:539,751
I could have worked overseas; Lord knows there was plenty of demand, but after seeing what my buddies went through in the last brushfire, I said, screw it, let me guard some fat CEO or worthless, dumb celebrity.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[92]:751,804
And that’s where I found myself when the Panic hit.
====
