====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[106]:0,88
It was bedlam, exactly what you thought the end of the world was supposed to look like.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[106]:88,198
Part of the house was burning, blood everywhere, bodies or bits of them spewed over all that expensive stuff.
