====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[106]:535,664
We’d been paid to protect rich people from zombies, not against other not-so-rich people who just wanted a safe place to hide.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[106]:664,736
You could hear them shouting as they charged in through the front door.
