A lot of them were from Sunbelt states, some as far away as southern Mexico.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:328,458
You’d see people getting into their sleeping bags with their boots on, not realizing that it was cutting off their circulation.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:458,583
You’d see them drinking to get warm, not realizing it was actually lowering their temperature by releasing more body heat.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:583,669
You’d see them wearing these big heavy coats with nothing but a T-shirt underneath.
====
