They’d do something physical, overheat, take off the coat.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:730,814
Their bodies’d be coated in sweat, a lot of cotton cloth holding in the moisture.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:814,886
The breeze’d come up…a lot of people got sick that first September.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:886,900
Cold and flu.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[313]:900,931
They gave it to the rest of us.
