====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[314]:678,740
They weren’t smart like us.” He’d try to force a smile.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[314]:740,783
For a little while, I thought he was right.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[315]:0,127
But after the first month, when the food started running out, and the days got colder and darker, people started getting mean.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[315]:127,191
There were no more communal fires, no more cookouts or singing.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[315]:191,254
