====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[315]:254,294
A couple times I stepped in human shit.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[315]:294,331
Nobody was even bothering to bury it.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:0,80
I wasn’t left alone with neighbors anymore, my parents didn’t trust anyone.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:80,131
Things got dangerous, you’d see a lot of fights.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:131,205
I saw two women wrestling over a fur coat, tore it right down the middle.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:205,321
I saw one guy catching another guy trying to steal some stuff out of his car and beat his head in with a tire iron.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:321,376
A lot of it took place at night, scuffling and shouts.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:376,440
Every now and then you’d hear a gunshot, and somebody crying.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:440,532
One time we heard someone moving outside the makeshift tent we’d draped over the minivan.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:532,583
Mom told me to put my head down and cover my ears.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[316]:583,601
Dad went outside.
====
