====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[325]:942,1157
She said “it” wasn’t “that bad” because the neighbors, not us, had been the ones to actually “do it.” Dad said that we weren’t going to stoop to that level and that Mom should be ashamed of herself.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[325]:1157,1257
Mom really laid into Dad, screeching that it was all his fault that we were here, that I was dying.
====
