/html/body/div/div[5]/p[380]
TAOS, NEW MEXICO
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[381]:0,142
[Arthur Sinclair, Junior, is the picture of an old-world patrician: tall, lean, with close-cropped white hair and an affected Harvard accent.
====
/html/body/div/div[5]/p[381]:142,220
He speaks into the ether, rarely making eye contact or pausing for questions.
====
