/html/body/div/p[167]:57,167
The beam was a weaponized version of solid-state, industrial lasers, the kind used to cut steel in factories.
====
/html/body/div/p[167]:167,280
It could either burn through a bomb’s outer casing or heat it to a point that detonated the explosive package.
====
/html/body/div/p[167]:280,319
