====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[19]:403,493
Last month a cargo plane nearing their airspace was fired on by a surface-to-air missile.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[19]:493,629
The launcher was an automated model, the type they’d designed as a revenge weapon in case the population had already been obliterated.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:0,86
Conventional wisdom is that they must have evacuated to their subterranean complexes.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:86,188
If that is true, then our estimates of the size and depth of those complexes were grossly inaccurate.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:188,380
Maybe the entire population is underground, tooling away on endless war projects, while their “Great Leader” continues to anesthetize himself with Western liquor and American pornography.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:380,415
Do they even know the war is over?
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:415,518
Have their leaders lied to them, again, and told them that the world as they know it has ceased to be?
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:518,667
Maybe the rise of the dead was a “good” thing in their eyes, an excuse to tighten the yoke even further in a society built on blind subjugation.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:667,897
The Great Leader always wanted to be a living God, and now, as master not only of the food his people eat, the air they breathe, but the very light of their artificial suns, maybe his twisted fantasy has finally become a reality.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[20]:897,970
Maybe that was the original plan, but something went disastrously wrong.
====
