I went into the kitchen area, grabbed some raw ramen, and ran back to my desk.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[35]:890,945
I did it again, that night, and again the next morning.
====
/html/body/div/div[7]/p[36]
You never questioned where your parents were?
====
