====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[70]:393,492
He knew it might have jeopardized everything, however, and reluctantly gave the order to cast off.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[70]:492,588
He tried to hide his feelings and I think, in front of most, he might have gotten away with it.
====
