====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[90]:0,254
There were so many beat-up hulks that should have been retired years ago: skiffs, ferries, and lighters that had spent their careers on quiet lakes or inland rivers, coastal crafts that should have never left the harbor for which they’d been designed.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[90]:254,407
