/html/body/div/div[15]/p[340]
 
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[341]:0,34
Pure bloods were a total washout.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[341]:34,158
Too neurotic, too many health problems, everything you’d expect from breeding an animal for just its aesthetic qualities.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[341]:158,304
The new generation [he gestures to the mutt on his lap] was always a mix, whatever would increase both physical constitution and mental stability.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[342]
 
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[343]:0,28
[The dog has gone to sleep.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[343]:28,54
Darnell lowers his voice.]
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[344]
 
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[345]:0,106
They were tough, took a lot of training, not just individually but for working in groups on LRP missions.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[345]:106,166
Long range, especially over wild terrain, was always risky.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[345]:166,210
Not just from Zack, but also from feral Ks.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[345]:210,238
