/html/body/div/div[15]/p[365]:353,573
For the first time the army saw us as teams, that a dog wasn’t just a piece of machinery you could replace when “broken.” They started looking at statistics of handlers who offed themselves after losing a partner.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[365]:573,650
You know we had the highest rate of suicide among any branch of the service.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[365]:650,754
More than Special Forces, more than Graves Registration, even more than those sick fucks at China Lake.
