====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[466]:1296,1373
Before she could be raised, we had to do a compartment-by-compartment sweep.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[466]:1373,1431
That was the only time the exo ever felt bulky, unwieldy.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[466]:1431,1511
I didn’t smack my head in every passageway, but it sure as hell felt like it.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[466]:1511,1556
