====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[551]:503,542
Slow and safe, like most major cities.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[551]:542,550
Why us?
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[551]:550,638
That English general, what he said about “Enough dead heroes for the end of time…”
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[552]:0,114
“Heroes,” that’s what we were, that’s what our leaders wanted, that’s what our people felt they needed.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[552]:114,288
After all that has happened, not just in this war, but in so many wars before: Algeria, Indochina, the Nazis…you understand what I am saying…you see the sorrow and pity?
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[552]:288,407
We understood what the American president said about “reclaiming our confidence”; we understood it more than most.
