====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[553]:91,216
The Nazis had built it to house mental patients, so the legend goes, letting them starve to death behind the concrete walls.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[553]:216,281
During our war it had been an infirmary for the recently bitten.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[553]:281,460
