/html/body/div/div[15]/p[562]:191,384
Just sitting there in zero visibility, occasionally one of your Ks would start barking or a man down the line would shout “Contact!” You’d hear the moan and then the shapes would appear.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[562]:384,438
Hard enough just standing still and waiting for them.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[562]:438,555
