====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[562]:681,730
They didn’t need that extra creepy soundtrack.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[562]:730,764
2 It freaked me out just to watch.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[563]:0,96
It also slowed us down to have to keep pace with the other countries, the Mexicans and Canucks.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[563]:96,160
Neither army had the manpower to liberate their entire country.
====
