====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[587]:389,428
Sure you didn’t need rescuing, buddy.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:0,23
Sometimes it was true.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:23,58
Like the zoomies outside of Omaha.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:58,134
They were a strategic hub for airdrops, regular flights almost on the hour.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:134,212
They were actually living better than us, fresh chow, hot showers, soft beds.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:212,255
It almost felt like we were being rescued.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:255,311
On the other hand, you had the jarheads at Rock Island.
====
