They wouldn’t let on how rough they had it, and that was cool with us.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:384,462
For what they went through, bragging rights was the least we could give them.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[588]:462,525
Never met any of them personally, but I’ve heard the stories.
====
