/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:121,160
There was no cheering, no celebration.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:160,188
It just didn’t seem real.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:188,195
Peace?
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:195,224
What the hell did that mean?
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:224,364
I’d been afraid for so long, fighting and killing, and waiting to die, that I guess I just accepted it as normal for the rest of my life.
====
/html/body/div/div[15]/p[759]:364,479
I thought it was a dream, sometimes it still feels like one, remembering that day, that sunrise over the Hero City.
====
